quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  3,42,"Tuma nde Malaa'ika en wi'unoo: \"Hey Maryama, pellet Alla SuЙ“ike ma, O LaЙ“Й“inii ma [O SuЙ“ii] e rewЙ“e winndere nden"
  3,43,"Hey Maryam, toЖґЖґinano Joomi maa, sujjaa ruЖґЖґidaa e ruЖґЖґooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,44,"ЖЉum Й—oo, ko jeyaaЙ—um e kumpite wirniiЙ—e, MeЙ—en Wahayina Й—e e maaЙ—a. A tawanooka e maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e weddotonoo kuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in: ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e ne'ata Maryama; a tawanooka e maЙ“Й“e kadi nde Й“e wennjaynoo"
  3,45,"Nde Malaa'ika en wi'unoo: \"Hey Maryama, Alla no Wewlinire Konngol immorde e Maako: Innde makko, ko meema-sella, Iisaa geЙ—al Maryama, koohoojo aduna e laakara, jeyaaЙ—a e Й“aЙ—tinaaЙ“e [ka Alla]"
  3,46,"Himo yeewtida e yimЙ“e Й“en ka woofordu=tiggu e ka sagatalaaku, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖґЖґuЙ“e Й“en"
  3,47,"O wi'i: \"Joomi am, hol no Й“iЙ—Й—o laatoraЕ‹ta lam, Й“anndiЕ‹ke meemaali lam?\". O Daali: \"Ko wano non. Alla no Taga ko O Muuyi. Si O Г‘aawii fiyaake, O Daalanay mo [tun]: \"Laato! o laatoo"
  3,48,Himo Anndina mo Deftere nden e Г‘eeГ±al ngal e Tawreeta e Linnjiila
  3,49,"E NulaaЙ—o faade e Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila en, wonnde: \"GomЙ—ii mi addanii on maande immorde ka Joomi mon. Wonnde miЙ—o tagana on immorde e loopal ko wa'i wa sonndu, mi wutta e muuЙ—um woЕ‹tira sonndu e DuЕ‹ayee Alla. Mi wumtina bunЙ—o, mi sellina baadaaЙ—o, mi wuurnitira maayЙ“e e duЕ‹ayee Alla. Mi humpita on ko Г±aamoton e ko maroton ka cuuЙ—i mon. Pellet, hino e Й—um, maande wonanannde on si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  3,50,"e goonginЙ—o ko woni yeeso am immorde e Tawreeta, e no mi dagininirana on yoga e ko harmannoo on, mi addanii on maande immorde ka Joomi mon. Hulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on lam"
  3,51,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon, rewee Mo. Ko Й—um woni laawol focciingol"
  3,52,"Tuma nde Iisaa so'unoo keeferaaku ngun e maЙ“Й“e, o maaki: \"Ko hommbo wallata lam e [diina] Alla [kan]?\". HawaaruyaЕ‹ko en wi'i: \"Menen ko men wallooЙ“e [e diina] Alla [kan], men gomЙ—inii Alla, seedo wonnde ko men jebbiiliiЙ“e"
  3,53,"Joomi amen, men gomЙ—inii ko JipinЙ—aa Kon, men jokkii NulaaЙ—o on, Winndu men e seediiЙ“e Й“en"
  3,54,ЖЃe fewji Alla Kadi Fewji. Ko Alla ЖЃuri MoЖґЖґude e fewjooЙ“e Й“en